1
00:00:00,300 --> 00:00:01,933
welcome back everyone

2
00:00:02,333 --> 00:00:04,633
today with the help of gigachad

3
00:00:04,800 --> 00:00:07,100
we are going to make an eye of Harmony

4
00:00:07,666 --> 00:00:12,466
Eye of harmony is one quite complex and expensive endgame multi block

5
00:00:12,466 --> 00:00:16,533
which is required for making UXV parts and progress further

6
00:00:16,933 --> 00:00:21,500
the first thing we are going to do with it is condensed raw stellar plasma mixture

7
00:00:21,500 --> 00:00:26,700

which is used for making magnetohydrodynamical constrained star matter


8
00:00:27,500 --> 00:00:30,200
which is used in every UXV item

9
00:00:30,733 --> 00:00:34,266
however making such machine is no easy task

10
00:00:34,266 --> 00:00:39,433
here you can see just a few of the crafting step of just a few of its structure

11
00:00:39,500 --> 00:00:42,466
and we also had to expand our crypto farm

12
00:00:42,466 --> 00:00:44,933
and the power capacity of our research station

13
00:00:44,933 --> 00:00:47,200
for researching such machinery

14
00:00:47,300 --> 00:00:49,233
but this was still not enough

15
00:00:49,466 --> 00:00:53,933
we had to tweak almost every part of our base to handle such task

16
00:00:53,933 --> 00:00:57,300
and we moved to wireless energy almost everywhere

17
00:00:57,666 --> 00:01:01,100
we upgraded multiple times our circuitry setups

18
00:01:02,400 --> 00:01:06,266
we had to find and work around different kinds of bottlenecks

19
00:01:06,433 --> 00:01:10,200
and we reached really high circuit production speeds

20
00:01:10,466 --> 00:01:12,866
we built some more space elevators

21
00:01:12,866 --> 00:01:17,266
for all the required materials and space processing required

22
00:01:17,333 --> 00:01:20,400
we did some tinkering with our new computers

23
00:01:20,866 --> 00:01:23,200
to lose less Dyson modules

24
00:01:23,600 --> 00:01:26,133
and made a few more Dyson spheres

25
00:01:26,733 --> 00:01:29,333
we unlocked the glowing fusion reactors

26
00:01:30,266 --> 00:01:34,133
and also added some glitter to the mega blast furnaces

27
00:01:35,033 --> 00:01:38,133
and we must not forget about our nanites production

28
00:01:38,133 --> 00:01:40,133
let's have more nano forges

29
00:01:40,800 --> 00:01:44,066
anyways now that the preparations are ready

30
00:01:44,100 --> 00:01:46,933
it's time to start working on that beast

31
00:01:47,333 --> 00:01:48,600
as you can see

32
00:01:48,600 --> 00:01:52,666
its structure requires a lot of slow assembly line recipes

33
00:01:54,466 --> 00:01:58,233
and thus we have started making more assembly lines

34
00:02:00,600 --> 00:02:02,800
and we finally have completed it

35
00:02:03,100 --> 00:02:06,600
this may not look that big when compared to other multi blocks

36
00:02:06,600 --> 00:02:10,400
but if we get close and go inside it

37
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:15,300
we can realize it contains a pocket of space time large enough to fit a planet

38
00:02:15,933 --> 00:02:17,700
however fear not

39
00:02:17,933 --> 00:02:23,133

this multi-block is compliant with Time Lords' regulations and certifications


40
00:02:24,500 --> 00:02:29,300
the thing we should be worrying about is the astounding amount of stuff it can output

41
00:02:30,466 --> 00:02:33,633
and since this one has been overclocked too much

42
00:02:33,633 --> 00:02:35,466
we now have two issues

43
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:39,466
as you can see we have a lot of buffered resources

44
00:02:39,633 --> 00:02:41,233
too many resources

45
00:02:42,300 --> 00:02:47,500
and the reason why these are not being taken is because we clogged our AE2 system

46
00:02:47,933 --> 00:02:52,200
normal disks can only contain up to 140 million items

47
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:56,833
and the output bus seems to not like outputting into quantum chests

48
00:02:57,266 --> 00:03:01,500
and thus we had to start using digital singularity cells

49
00:03:02,100 --> 00:03:04,433
and so we are stocking up items

50
00:03:05,066 --> 00:03:07,333
the second issue is the power eating

51
00:03:08,300 --> 00:03:12,733
we have been forced into turning on out backup generator

52
00:03:12,733 --> 00:03:18,000
and even though the first time the issue was just the excessive overclock amount

53
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:22,633
we still wanted to make sure we could safely afford a second eye of harmony

54
00:03:22,633 --> 00:03:25,333
so we made a few more Dyson Spheres

55
00:03:26,066 --> 00:03:28,266
and here we have the second eye

56
00:03:29,833 --> 00:03:34,100
this time the structure has been built to support tier 4 planets

57
00:03:34,100 --> 00:03:36,866
so that we can produce black dwarf matter

58
00:03:37,933 --> 00:03:42,000
this time we also had to do some more tinkering with the fluids

59
00:03:43,633 --> 00:03:47,400
the next tiers of eye of harmony are going to take a lot of time

60
00:03:47,433 --> 00:03:51,300
so let's use this time to do some cleaning of our base

61
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,266
and in that time

62
00:04:42,300 --> 00:04:45,033
we have managed to build a 7th tier of eye

63
00:04:45,800 --> 00:04:49,266
which now contains one whole solar system

64
00:04:49,533 --> 00:04:52,333
and it can produce molten universium

65
00:04:53,033 --> 00:04:56,400
which is one of the components of UXV parts

66
00:04:57,100 --> 00:05:02,333
the other component is the magneto hydrodynamical constrained star matter parts

67
00:05:02,333 --> 00:05:07,133
which are made in an implosion compressor with weird things like an hologram projector

68
00:05:07,666 --> 00:05:09,433
but before that

69
00:05:09,433 --> 00:05:12,300
let's unlock the last tier of eye of harmony

70
00:05:12,300 --> 00:05:14,333
the research is going super fast

71
00:05:14,333 --> 00:05:19,700
thanks both to the video speed up and our new Accelerated Processing units

72
00:05:20,500 --> 00:05:22,900
and after one more fix

73
00:05:24,333 --> 00:05:30,066
we have finally managed to serialize the block for the most powerful version of eye of harmony

74
00:05:30,666 --> 00:05:34,000
it might looks like this crafting is going super fast

75
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:36,700
and that's because we have done a lot of overclocks

76
00:05:36,700 --> 00:05:40,400
other than the 16x bonus of the parallelization

77
00:05:41,266 --> 00:05:45,300
however, we run out of universium for completing the project

78
00:05:46,533 --> 00:05:49,266
and making more takes either a lot of time

79
00:05:50,033 --> 00:05:51,300
or a lot of energy

80
00:05:51,633 --> 00:05:57,033
so the way to make that recipe feasible is to reduce the overclocking settings

81
00:05:57,533 --> 00:06:00,966
and replace the time dilatation fields generators

82
00:06:00,966 --> 00:06:06,433
that will decrease the time taken by magnitudes at the cost of success chance

83
00:06:07,400 --> 00:06:10,666
and thus we are capable of producing some universium

84
00:06:10,733 --> 00:06:14,800
however we only succeed once every four times

85
00:06:15,200 --> 00:06:19,266
so we are going to make some stabilization field generators

86
00:06:19,733 --> 00:06:23,733
these will increase the odds and the energy output at the cost of yield

87
00:06:24,833 --> 00:06:27,666
and it was then that we run into an old issue

88
00:06:28,433 --> 00:06:31,233
our ae2 system is clogged again

89
00:06:31,866 --> 00:06:35,333
so we made even more singularity storage cells

90
00:06:35,333 --> 00:06:38,500
these are the only way to manage an eye of harmony

91
00:06:39,133 --> 00:06:42,433
and thanks to the new field generators

92
00:06:42,433 --> 00:06:46,233
we have finally managed to make a power positive eye of harmony

93
00:06:46,233 --> 00:06:48,633
which also produces resources

94
00:06:49,633 --> 00:06:51,433
now that we have universium

95
00:06:51,466 --> 00:06:56,400
we can finally craft the last tier of field generators - Gallifreyan

96
00:06:57,700 --> 00:07:00,633
so that we can finally harness the deep dark

97
00:07:01,433 --> 00:07:03,033
and this is the result

98
00:07:03,433 --> 00:07:06,200
we now have 10 planets spinning inside

99
00:07:06,633 --> 00:07:08,666
and with 8 overclocks

100
00:07:09,133 --> 00:07:13,866
it takes 90 seconds and 61 teraEU per tick

101
00:07:13,866 --> 00:07:19,100
to make an average of 13,000 molten universium

102
00:07:19,933 --> 00:07:22,466
or 2 petaEU for instant

103
00:07:24,400 --> 00:07:31,500
next we made a 2700 million CPU to craft the Gallifreyan stabilization fields

104
00:07:33,533 --> 00:07:37,533
meanwhile we run out of space and energy again

105
00:07:38,466 --> 00:07:41,400
but fear not that was for a good cause

106
00:07:41,400 --> 00:07:48,533
since we managed to finally make one eye of harmony which makes power and also resources at the same time

107
00:07:48,933 --> 00:07:51,066
we get our cake and to eat it too

108
00:07:52,066 --> 00:07:58,533
next we swiftly craft each UXV part to have access to every part that can currently be crafted

109
00:07:59,900 --> 00:08:02,133
now that we have unlocked everything

110
00:08:02,133 --> 00:08:06,200
it is time to finally start working on the final destination

111
00:08:06,833 --> 00:08:09,300
for the quest, we need just one plate

112
00:08:09,300 --> 00:08:11,400
but we are going to need way more

113
00:08:12,233 --> 00:08:14,266
and just by looking at the recipe

114
00:08:14,266 --> 00:08:18,533
we start to realize that we might need to do some more preparations

115
00:08:19,866 --> 00:08:24,333
still let's start working on it just to see how it goes

116
00:08:25,133 --> 00:08:27,666
the first thing is going to be the research

117
00:08:29,066 --> 00:08:31,633
and since this will take some time

118
00:08:31,633 --> 00:08:36,500
let's see how ae2 handles the materials for the actual crafting

119
00:08:37,466 --> 00:08:40,733
it looks like we have everything required for the task

120
00:08:40,733 --> 00:08:45,433
however with the current state of our factory that would take way too long

121
00:08:46,066 --> 00:08:49,400
so instead of slowly building one piece

122
00:08:49,400 --> 00:08:53,200
we shall not do that, and focus on first improving our base

123
00:08:53,233 --> 00:08:54,833
we have not enough machines

124
00:08:54,833 --> 00:08:58,200
and they are too much mixed around and on various tiers

125
00:08:58,200 --> 00:09:01,200
we want to have them all sorted out and at the max tier

126
00:09:01,266 --> 00:09:03,700
so let's do some tidying

127
00:09:53,633 --> 00:09:56,300
and now we can do our first test run

128
00:09:56,833 --> 00:09:59,466
and once all the parts are ready

129
00:09:59,500 --> 00:10:02,900
we can start the dedicated advanced assembly line

130
00:10:03,233 --> 00:10:08,500
we are going to use the first plate we made to research the next part we are going to need

131
00:10:08,600 --> 00:10:10,733
and after a lot of time

132
00:10:10,733 --> 00:10:13,000
we have the next recipe unlocked

133
00:10:13,800 --> 00:10:16,533
however our base is still not ready

134
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:20,233
since we drained all of our energy just for this test run

135
00:10:21,566 --> 00:10:24,033
so we added a bunch more of them

136
00:10:24,700 --> 00:10:27,466
and now we have a positive energy production

137
00:10:27,933 --> 00:10:32,233
all we have to do now is make circuits in bulks of 1 million

138
00:10:32,233 --> 00:10:35,466
then we do a bunch more of craftings with ae2

139
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:39,000
we do some occasional debugging and plumbing

140
00:10:39,066 --> 00:10:45,233
such as the dtpf getting stuck due to reaching the limit of catalyst accumulated by the discounts

141
00:10:45,800 --> 00:10:49,400
and once everything is working nicely and fine

142
00:10:49,400 --> 00:10:51,300
after some AFK time

143
00:10:51,300 --> 00:10:54,066
we can manually craft the Stargate base

144
00:10:54,266 --> 00:10:57,400
we do that manually to increase the value of the block

145
00:10:57,600 --> 00:11:01,533
who wants an artifact such as that to be made in an industrial way

146
00:11:02,100 --> 00:11:05,666
I'm not going to show you all the crazy work that ae2 did

147
00:11:05,666 --> 00:11:08,000
but that's the leftovers

148
00:11:08,933 --> 00:11:11,933
and after about 4 months of AFK

149
00:11:11,933 --> 00:11:14,900
we have finally managed to get the last part

150
00:11:16,333 --> 00:11:21,800
now we can finally claim the reward for the highest task one can do in this pack

151
00:11:21,800 --> 00:11:24,333
4 iron ingots and 3 sticks

152
00:11:24,833 --> 00:11:28,466
the only task left to do is to find out how to assemble it

153
00:11:28,466 --> 00:11:31,500
since there isn't much documentation on it

154
00:11:31,633 --> 00:11:36,233
and after many trials, we managed to make it work finally

155
00:11:36,300 --> 00:11:41,066
and it turns out that with only one Stargate we are going nowhere

156
00:11:41,066 --> 00:11:42,866
time to get back to work

157
00:00:00,300 --> 00:00:01,933
欢迎回来，各位

158
00:00:02,333 --> 00:00:04,633
今天在gigachad的帮助下

159
00:00:04,800 --> 00:00:07,100
我们要做鸿蒙之眼

160
00:00:07,666 --> 00:00:12,466
鸿蒙之眼是一个相当复杂和昂贵的大后期多方块

161
00:00:12,466 --> 00:00:16,533
而它是制造UXV部件和进一步发展所必需的

162
00:00:16,933 --> 00:00:21,500
我们要做的第一件东西是浓缩原始恒星等离子体混合物

163
00:00:21,500 --> 00:00:26,700
用于制造磁流体约束恒星物质

164
00:00:27,500 --> 00:00:30,200
它将用于每个UXV物品的制造

165
00:00:30,733 --> 00:00:34,266
然而制造这样的机器并非易事

166
00:00:34,266 --> 00:00:39,433

你欣赏一下它的几个结构方块的制作步骤


167
00:00:39,500 --> 00:00:42,466
我们还必须升级算力

168
00:00:42,466 --> 00:00:44,933
以及研究站的发电能力

169
00:00:44,933 --> 00:00:47,200
才能研究这种机器

170
00:00:47,300 --> 00:00:49,233
但这还不够

171
00:00:49,466 --> 00:00:53,933
我们不得不调整基地几乎
每一个部分来处理这样的任务

172
00:00:53,933 --> 00:00:57,300

我们几乎给所有机器用上了无线能源
 

173
00:00:57,666 --> 00:01:01,100
我们多次升级电路板自动化

174
00:01:02,400 --> 00:01:06,266

我们发现各种瓶颈问题，解决它们


175
00:01:06,433 --> 00:01:10,200
我们达到了很高的电路生产速度

176
00:01:10,466 --> 00:01:12,866
我们又造了一些太空电梯

177
00:01:12,866 --> 00:01:17,266
用于所有所需的材料和太空处理

178
00:01:17,333 --> 00:01:20,400
我们对新电脑做了些修补

179
00:01:20,866 --> 00:01:23,200
以损失更少的戴森模块

180
00:01:23,600 --> 00:01:26,133
并多做了几个戴森球

181
00:01:26,733 --> 00:01:29,333
我们解锁了发光的聚变反应堆

182
00:01:30,266 --> 00:01:34,133
并在巨高炉中添加了一些闪光

183
00:01:35,033 --> 00:01:38,133

纳米蜂群的生产也不能忘


184
00:01:38,133 --> 00:01:40,133
让我们造更多的纳米锻炉

185
00:01:40,800 --> 00:01:44,066
不管怎样，现在准备工作已经好了

186
00:01:44,100 --> 00:01:46,933
是时候开始对付那只野兽了

187
00:01:47,333 --> 00:01:48,600
如你所见

188
00:01:48,600 --> 00:01:52,666
它的结构需要很多缓慢的装配线配方

189
00:01:54,466 --> 00:01:58,233
因此我们开始制造更多的装配线

190
00:02:00,600 --> 00:02:02,800
我们终于完成了它

191
00:02:03,100 --> 00:02:06,600
与其他多方块相比，这可能看起来没那么大

192
00:02:06,600 --> 00:02:10,400
但如果我们飞进去

193
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:15,300
我们意识到它能装下一整颗行星

194
00:02:15,933 --> 00:02:17,700
但不要害怕

195
00:02:17,933 --> 00:02:23,133

此多方块符合时间领主的规定和认证


196
00:02:24,500 --> 00:02:29,300
我们应该担心的是
它输出的惊人数量的东西

197
00:02:30,466 --> 00:02:33,633
由于它超频了太多

198
00:02:33,633 --> 00:02:35,466
我们现在有两个问题

199
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:39,466
如你所见，它缓存了很多东西

200
00:02:39,633 --> 00:02:41,233
过于多的东西

201
00:02:42,300 --> 00:02:47,500
这些东西没有进AE的原因是
AE系统已经爆满

202
00:02:47,933 --> 00:02:52,200
普通磁盘最多只能装下1.40亿个东西

203
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:56,833
输出总线似乎不喜欢输出到量子箱

204
00:02:57,266 --> 00:03:01,500
因此，我们必须开始使用数字奇点单元

205
00:03:02,100 --> 00:03:04,433

这样我们就能存下很多东西了


206
00:03:05,066 --> 00:03:07,333
第二个问题是电力消耗

207
00:03:08,300 --> 00:03:12,733
我们被迫打开备用发电机

208
00:03:12,733 --> 00:03:18,000
尽管第一次的问题只是超频量过大

209
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:22,633

我们仍然想确保我们能安全地
负担起第二只鸿蒙之眼的消耗


210
00:03:22,633 --> 00:03:25,333
所以我们又做了几个戴森球

211
00:03:26,066 --> 00:03:28,266
这就是第二个EoH

212
00:03:29,833 --> 00:03:34,100

这次建造的结构能容纳四级行星


213
00:03:34,100 --> 00:03:36,866
这样我们才能产生黑矮星物质

214
00:03:37,933 --> 00:03:42,000
这一次，我们还必须对液体进行更多的处理

215
00:03:43,633 --> 00:03:47,400
鸿蒙之眼的下一级要花很多时间

216
00:03:47,433 --> 00:03:51,300
所以让我们利用这段时间来清理基地

217
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,266
在这段时间里

218
00:04:42,300 --> 00:04:45,033
我们成功建造了第7级的EoH

219
00:04:45,800 --> 00:04:49,266
现在它包含了一个完整的太阳系

220
00:04:49,533 --> 00:04:52,333
它可以产生熔融宇宙素

221
00:04:53,033 --> 00:04:56,400
这是UXV零件的一部分

222
00:04:57,100 --> 00:05:02,333
另一部分是磁流体约束恒星物质

223
00:05:02,333 --> 00:05:07,133

它们是在聚爆压缩机中放入
类似全息投影仪这种奇怪的东西制造的


224
00:05:07,666 --> 00:05:09,433
但在那之前

225
00:05:09,433 --> 00:05:12,300
让我们解锁最后一级的鸿蒙之眼

226
00:05:12,300 --> 00:05:14,333
研究进展得非常快

227
00:05:14,333 --> 00:05:19,700
这得感谢剪辑加速和新的APU

228
00:05:20,500 --> 00:05:22,900
再经过一次修复后

229
00:05:24,333 --> 00:05:30,066
我们终于成功并行制造了
满级鸿蒙之眼的结构方块

230
00:05:30,666 --> 00:05:34,000
这个合成看起来似乎非常快

231
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:37,733
那是因为除了并行的16倍加成

232
00:05:37,733 --> 00:05:40,400
我们还做了很多超频

233
00:05:41,266 --> 00:05:45,300
然而，我们用完了这个项目所需的宇宙素

234
00:05:46,533 --> 00:05:49,266
制造更多的宇宙素需要很多时间

235
00:05:50,033 --> 00:05:51,300
或者很多能量

236
00:05:51,633 --> 00:05:57,033
因此，使该配方可行的方法是减少超频设置

237
00:05:57,533 --> 00:06:00,966
并更换时间膨胀场发生器

238
00:06:00,966 --> 00:06:06,433
这将以成功概率为代价减少大量时间

239
00:06:07,400 --> 00:06:10,666
这样，我们就有能力生产宇宙素

240
00:06:10,733 --> 00:06:14,800
然而我们的配方每四次才成功一次

241
00:06:15,200 --> 00:06:19,266
所以我们要做一些稳定场发生器

242
00:06:19,733 --> 00:06:23,733
这些将增加配方成功几率
和能量输出，但代价是产量降低

243
00:06:24,833 --> 00:06:27,666
就在这时，我们遇到了老问题

244
00:06:28,433 --> 00:06:31,233
我们的AE系统又堵塞了

245
00:06:31,866 --> 00:06:35,333
所以我们制造了更多的奇点存储单元

246
00:06:35,333 --> 00:06:38,500
这些是管理鸿蒙之眼输出的唯一方法

247
00:06:39,133 --> 00:06:42,433
多亏了新的稳定场发生器

248
00:06:42,433 --> 00:06:46,233
我们总算成功创造了一个能发电的鸿蒙之眼

249
00:06:46,233 --> 00:06:48,633
它也产生了很多资源

250
00:06:49,633 --> 00:06:51,433
现在我们有宇宙素了

251
00:06:51,466 --> 00:06:56,400
我们终于可以制造最后一级的场发生器了

252
00:06:57,700 --> 00:07:00,633

这样我们就能收获深暗世界的资源


253
00:07:01,433 --> 00:07:03,033
这就是做出来的样子

254
00:07:03,433 --> 00:07:06,200
我们现在有10颗行星在里面旋转

255
00:07:06,633 --> 00:07:08,666
并带有8次超频

256
00:07:09,133 --> 00:07:13,866
它将花费90秒和61万亿EU/t

257
00:07:13,866 --> 00:07:19,100
平均制造1.3万L的熔融宇宙素

258
00:07:19,933 --> 00:07:22,466
或者一口气用 2e15 EU

259
00:07:24,400 --> 00:07:31,500
接下来，我们制作一个27亿容量
的CPU来制作鸿蒙稳定场

260
00:07:33,533 --> 00:07:37,533
与此同时，我们又耗尽了主网空间和电量

261
00:07:38,466 --> 00:07:41,400
别慌，这可是个好兆头

262
00:07:41,400 --> 00:07:48,533
因为这个EoH同时产出电量与资源

263
00:07:48,933 --> 00:07:51,066
我们真正地“自食其果”

264
00:07:52,066 --> 00:07:58,533
接下来，我们快速制作当前可获得的所有UXV部件

265
00:07:59,900 --> 00:08:02,133
既然我们已经解锁了一切

266
00:08:02,133 --> 00:08:06,200
是时候开始研究最终目的地了

267
00:08:06,833 --> 00:08:09,300
为了任务，我们只需要一个盘子

268
00:08:09,300 --> 00:08:11,400
但我们还会需要更多

269
00:08:12,233 --> 00:08:14,266
只要看看配方

270
00:08:14,266 --> 00:08:18,533
此时便可以意识到需要更多的准备

271
00:08:19,866 --> 00:08:24,333
还是让我们开始研究它，看看进展如何

272
00:08:25,133 --> 00:08:27,666
第一件事是研究

273
00:08:29,066 --> 00:08:31,633
因为这需要一些时间

274
00:08:31,633 --> 00:08:36,500
让我们看看AE如何处理实际制作的材料

275
00:08:37,466 --> 00:08:40,733
看起来任务所需的东西我们都有了

276
00:08:40,733 --> 00:08:45,433
然而，以我们工厂的现状，这需要太长时间

277
00:08:46,066 --> 00:08:49,400
所以与其慢慢地磨出一套来

278
00:08:49,400 --> 00:08:53,200
我们更倾向于升级基建

279
00:08:53,233 --> 00:08:54,833
我们机器太少

280
00:08:54,833 --> 00:08:58,200

它们各种电压都有


281
00:08:58,200 --> 00:09:01,200
让我们将其整理出来，全部换成最高电压

282
00:09:01,266 --> 00:09:03,700
所以让我们整理一下

283
00:09:53,633 --> 00:09:56,300
现在我们可以进行第一次试运行了

284
00:09:56,833 --> 00:09:59,466
一旦所有部件都准备好了

285
00:09:59,500 --> 00:10:02,900
我们可以启动专用的进阶装配线

286
00:10:03,233 --> 00:10:08,500
我们将使用我们制作的第一个盘子
来研究我们需要的下一个零件

287
00:10:08,600 --> 00:10:10,733
经过很长时间

288
00:10:10,733 --> 00:10:13,000
我们解锁了下一个配方

289
00:10:13,800 --> 00:10:16,533
然而我们的基地还没有准备好

290
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:20,233
因为我们为了这次测试耗尽了所有的电量

291
00:10:21,566 --> 00:10:24,033
所以我们又加了一堆

292
00:10:24,700 --> 00:10:27,466
现在我们有一个正的能量产出

293
00:10:27,933 --> 00:10:32,233

我们现在只需要以100万为单位下单电路板


294
00:10:32,233 --> 00:10:35,466

然后借助AE再多做一些合成工作


295
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:39,000
我们偶尔做一些调试和疏通管道

296
00:10:39,066 --> 00:10:45,233
如dtpf因达到折扣累积的催化剂极限而卡住

297
00:10:45,800 --> 00:10:49,400
一旦一切正常

298
00:10:49,400 --> 00:10:51,300
挂机一段时间后

299
00:10:51,300 --> 00:10:54,066
我们可以手动合成星门基座

300
00:10:54,266 --> 00:10:57,400

手搓这个方块以增加它的价值


301
00:10:57,600 --> 00:11:01,533
谁会希望这样的神器以工业化的方式制造出来

302
00:11:02,100 --> 00:11:05,666
我不会向你展示AE所做的所有疯狂工作

303
00:11:05,666 --> 00:11:08,000
但那是剩下的东西了

304
00:11:08,933 --> 00:11:11,933
挂机4个月后

305
00:11:11,933 --> 00:11:14,900
我们终于设法完成了最后一部分

306
00:11:16,333 --> 00:11:21,800
现在我们终于可以领取
这个整合包终极任务的奖励了

307
00:11:21,800 --> 00:11:24,333
4个铁锭和3根棍子

308
00:11:24,833 --> 00:11:28,466
剩下的唯一任务就是找出如何组装它

309
00:11:28,466 --> 00:11:31,500
因为没有多少操作说明

310
00:11:31,633 --> 00:11:36,233
经过多次试验我们终于成功了

311
00:11:36,300 --> 00:11:41,066
结果发现只有一个星门我们无处可去

312
00:11:41,066 --> 00:11:42,866
该回去工作了

313
00:07:48,933 --> 00:07:51,066
（上期the cake is a lie的callback）

